{"tid":2019554,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"現代導師Kris Lau 賄賂罪不成立 裁判官：僥倖脫罪","createTime":"2020-05-16T11:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T15:38:49.000Z","uid":223741,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92f39d060f10f1e37c6be4e06458801bcd615923","tid":2019554,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/451406275695774/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1448758471982883%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F451406275695774%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252F186040714921338%252Fposts%252F1448758471982883%252F%26_rdr&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=30ab30a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/451406275695774/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1448758471982883%2F&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n現代教育英文科導師劉冠華，3年前涉嫌賄賂考評局評卷助理取得試卷機密資料，罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官形容是僥倖脫罪，指兩人行為唔係可疑咁簡單，只是未有證據證明犯案意圖。"},{"pid":"3b1f5926ba18eadf49fe8f79704804ce2e9d924d","tid":2019554,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"In kris Lau we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f09b31afd450c78bef5ba9bd5b0dc7439c5cf40","tid":2019554,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:07:42.000Z","msg":"補Kris Lau全科<br />\n5**不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85481b8d2de3ad0ea14b15217984d1b25d01bf6d","tid":2019554,"uid":37719,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"官都咁講,下年唔補唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c088af26550ff6549de748c05d1d6f2e602c0f","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"分唇撈驚嫲"},{"pid":"0fd95cc36e6f3a5edfab109a474d43a8775a0ab9","tid":2019554,"uid":223741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"85481b8d2de3ad0ea14b15217984d1b25d01bf6d","tid":2019554,"uid":37719,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"官都咁講,下年唔補唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"記得補全科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">除咗英文</span>"},{"pid":"8a80028e4c0d93559d3e40b7a53ffcb7a87eb0f0","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"問：有英文補習導師自稱是唯一學過 functional grammar的導師，這是什麼文法？我身為英文教師，都沒有聽過 functional grammar一詞。<br />\n<br />\n答：英文文法有 functional grammar、 transformational grammar、 generative grammar等等，從語文的實際功用（ function）、基本原則轉化（ transform）為句子表面結構、基本語法衍生（ generate）為無數同類型句子等專門角度論文法，和我們日常說的文法有別。除非你要做英文文法專家，否則這些文法學說不必理會。那位導師大概只是用 functional grammar一詞做噱頭而已。  <br />\n<br />\n古德明 <br />\nappledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"68e8d49075ea46fa5e84b16fbf6d35659f0d4176","tid":2019554,"uid":223741,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"Kris Lau 補習團隊由始至終不能收新插班自修生的原因： <br />\n<br />\n誰不知道有教無類？但我只是一個微小的人，不是神。 <br />\n微小如我，又怎能救贖中毒極深、冥頑不靈的人呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第一次機會 <br />\n每年 7 月放榜，我們都會有自己友狀元，5** 及 5* 的學生影相和獎學金派發。我教出全港末代高考第一名 6A1B，第一屆DSE 最高 5** 率，你對於補習沒有做過research，沒有認識我，是你錯過我的第一次機會。 <br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第二次機會 <br />\n學生補習為求學業進步，假設中四、五 7/8 月開始補暑期課程，到開學 9/10 月，你對DSE ENG 考試應該有不錯的認識和進步。同學之中總有突飛猛進的（通常是我學生），你不會打聽嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第三次機會 <br />\n到了 11/12 月，學校有形形式式的考試，你補了幾個月英文習都沒有進步，完全沒有機動性地坐以待斃，沒有想過轉 ENG 補習老師嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第四次機會 <br />\n過了新年，到了 1/2 月，校內又有形形式式的考試和MOCK，你的成績仍然沒有進步，現代有大量的Intensive 推廣，你居然沒有聽過Kris Lau 最高5** 率的名字，不知中了什麼毒，你選擇繼續，不轉英文補習老師。 <br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第五次機會 <br />\n校內MOCK 成績公布，我的學生通常名列前茅，現代有TIPS Class 的大型宣傳，這個時間我收了大量的新學生，但又不知你中了什麼毒，你選擇繼續中毒，不轉英文補習老師。 <br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第六次機會 <br />\n終於到了 3/4 月，真正的DSE 考試來了。Paper 1、2、3 我的學生在試場殺過片甲不留，他們在我Facebook 洗版，他們大部分是Band 1 學校的學生或Band 2 的三甲學生。他們大部分用自己真的Facebook account 在我的Facebook Wall 上留言，你可以隨意click 一 click 留言者Facebook 的背景，你就知道全部堅料。你選擇繼續中毒，不轉英文補習老師。 <br />\n<br />\n錯過我的第七次機會 <br />\nFacebook 世界中，我有最多Band 1 學生清晰指出我如何TIP 中。而作為老師的我，根本不需多講說話，因為 7 月放榜，我蟬聯最高 5** 率會告訴你一切！Paper 1、2、3 考得不好，還有Speaking Paper 4，你可有選擇報我的 Paper 4 Speaking？你選擇繼續中毒，不轉英文補習老師。 <br />\n<br />\n已經沒有機會 <br />\n由 5 月頭去到 5 月中，DSE 考英文 Paper 4 Speaking 如火如荼，我又是Facebook 世界中得到最多學界猛人誠實地用自己Facebook account 清晰地說明如何用我Speaking 技巧打贏所有對手的詳盡紀錄，有些還由Paper 1 開始講到Paper 4 打贏所有對手的詳盡紀錄，我所教過的強勁 paper 1-4 技巧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c992e22336b2fbda3a572f153979c84e91f9c03e","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"Kris Lau ielts 幾分？"},{"pid":"504928556e65f3491326374d8335e1587749c78d","tid":2019554,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c992e22336b2fbda3a572f153979c84e91f9c03e","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"Kris Lau ielts 幾分？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔敢挑戰"},{"pid":"c99e505f56ae57398d603778c166e79865f31843","tid":2019554,"uid":212599,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"我嗰陣去補 佢話我你英文等攞2啦 <br />\n之後即刻唔補<br />\n最後2017 DSE straight 5**<br />\nKris Lau 收皮啦 上堂hea到播舊片然後自己喺度挽手機"},{"pid":"603b38c6ffbf321857f11e4b2f45c40660a5c274","tid":2019554,"uid":34764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:16:41.000Z","msg":"條友大把錢請d勁既律師"},{"pid":"d35eba20bcd786a6a64f30aceb4b64370365c6da","tid":2019554,"uid":310933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c992e22336b2fbda3a572f153979c84e91f9c03e","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"Kris Lau ielts 幾分？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"7.0佢自己講"},{"pid":"02a993f901f053ccf93f3b234d3c59ecf545373e","tid":2019554,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"裁判官有立場"},{"pid":"b41a6df5755138e8e904599e0d2d3c2f42403aae","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d35eba20bcd786a6a64f30aceb4b64370365c6da","tid":2019554,"uid":310933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c992e22336b2fbda3a572f153979c84e91f9c03e","tid":2019554,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":